{"tid":2228614,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(跪求)solo leveling嘅小說係邊睇 我忍唔住啦 漫畫j死我","createTime":"2020-10-03T17:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T14:29:25.000Z","uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d941162653c86cf990b61721e306b6d407da8322","tid":2228614,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T17:09:11.000Z","msg":"我搵咗勁多都好似唔齊咁<br />\n因為漫畫講到好似有兩個王(?) 信息量有啲大 <br />\n所以想追小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求好心人share<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aU1gDKd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaU1gDKd.png&h=44003b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未睇過嘅jj都推薦入坑  一齊討論<br />\n故事係講<br />\n依個係有地下城嘅世界 有資格嘅人會成為獵人<br />\n男主係人類最弱兵器嘅E級獵人<br />\n有一次佢跟團進入D級地下城 <br />\n點知原來係雙重地下城(必為A級以上,而事實攻略難度係s級)<br />\n幾乎滅團 主角頻死之際 「系統」出現<br />\n得到「系統」嘅力量佢一步一步踏上王嘅寶座<br />\n成為傲視群雄嘅存在...<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">雙重地下城嘅恐怖天使雕像BOSS:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xrDR41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xrDR41.png&h=d7b657a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gmNLw43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgmNLw43.png&h=e1e69768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">弱爆男主慘遭虐殺：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Cf9e10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Cf9e10.png&h=32e50efe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lzm4Om2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzm4Om2.png&h=e8fffb1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7NWEtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7NWEtJ.png&h=d9b3a6c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">因為「系統」嘅賞識而得到成為「玩家」嘅機會:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JDyFZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JDyFZP.png&h=a08abef9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxUqw6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxUqw6x.png&h=6eaa6974&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho92zjT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho92zjT.png&h=bee83fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">努力升級嘅佢：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAzVbtr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAzVbtr.png&h=7625ddc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpkdHz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpkdHz9.png&h=3234cd6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">後來佢嘅能力令到其他s級獵人震驚:</span><br />\n(我當初就係喺群組見到依幾張圖入坑)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xzper2N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzper2N.png&h=777fa56f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwR4Pf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwR4Pf9.png&h=f5525995&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4ybuga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4ybuga.png&h=2ea2e172&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1Mwugc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1Mwugc.png&h=6e915181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">連公會自豪嘅「評審者」喺王面前只係一隻褸蟻：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59jh9gn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59jh9gn.png&h=c64d75da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOf1RuK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOf1RuK.png&h=b41d457e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J19FnBq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ19FnBq.png&h=898ff473&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvbsM27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvbsM27.png&h=4bb7a35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">由地底泥蜕變成擁有影子兵團嘅王：</span>(未完)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2w6THBC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2w6THBC.png&h=4c74d29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漫畫有漢化有英文有日文<br />\n任君選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人有小說介唔介意share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e84a7bb1bb37ca721b8ca228f54e6f87c6d8c3","tid":2228614,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T17:11:08.000Z","msg":"小說有台灣漢化當然最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無嘅話 英文都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8b946d87a9ced300fc2373ed98a484b51d9028","tid":2228614,"uid":141894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"有睇 好正<br />\n睇完中文版 再睇左次英文版漫畫<br />\n節奏明快 唔拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8b7677deae141d5e68f697d0f03ab89c8eda59","tid":2228614,"uid":141894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nightmyths.com/manga/only-i-level-up-solo-leveling/chapter-1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnightmyths.com%2Fmanga%2Fonly-i-level-up-solo-leveling%2Fchapter-1%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=9bf5acfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nightmyths.com/manga/only-i-level-up-solo-leveling/chapter-1/</a> <br />\n英文版小說<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇其他漫畫值得睇<br />\n最好有英譯版"},{"pid":"9f399d2c958d2403da255c018137ed310afd1d3d","tid":2228614,"uid":142770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢套真係好好睇"},{"pid":"118dcfbacc7e362c58ba3268cc4938fd7f8dec1b","tid":2228614,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n套小說係咪比支那封殺<br />\n完全搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2602cd03636e62882e47b40b0291447deb11ddbf","tid":2228614,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b8b7677deae141d5e68f697d0f03ab89c8eda59","tid":2228614,"uid":141894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nightmyths.com/manga/only-i-level-up-solo-leveling/chapter-1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnightmyths.com%2Fmanga%2Fonly-i-level-up-solo-leveling%2Fchapter-1%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=9bf5acfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nightmyths.com/manga/only-i-level-up-solo-leveling/chapter-1/</a> <br />\n英文版小說<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇其他漫畫值得睇<br />\n最好有英譯版"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T19:15:03.000Z","msg":"排名有分先後<br />\n<br />\n1.全知讀者視角(非常紅)<br />\n2.成為伯爵家的廢物<br />\n3.我培養的s級們<br />\n以上係被韓國讀者稱為小說三巨頭<br />\n全部已經拍板會製造動畫/電視劇<br />\n<br />\n睇弱弱主角逆襲無限開金手指<br />\n4.盜墓之王(有系統設定)<br />\n5.三歲開始成為王<br />\n6.重啟地下城(有系統設定)<br />\n<br />\n其他分類推介<br />\n看臉時代(入韓漫坑必睇)<br />\nSweet home(Netflix 買咗版權）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅極一時 開頭好睇開始爛尾類<br />\n神之塔<br />\n骰子<br />\n<br />\n我都係咁煲韓漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d1f7aa750b4447